<D>__{let me tell you something. i'm grateful for what he did.}
<P>__{(off her stunned look)}
<D>__{no kidding. every time i get an urge to play off the clock to so much as drop a quarter in a slot i reach down and squeeze what's left of my cartilage. it's one helluva reminder.}
