<D>__{jesus... i thought stuff like that didn't happen no more. like that was just in the movies or something.}
<A>__{bernie holds her gaze her for a moment.}
<C>__{bernie}
<D>__{anyway, shelly and i worked out a payment plan. two years off the books at the shangri la, cooling tables. five more days and i walk.}
